    "model": "claude-sonnet-4-6",
    "code": "t = int(input())\nfor _ in range(t):\n    n = int(input())\n    a = list(map(int, input().split()))\n    \n    best = float('inf')\n    \n    for c1 in range(3):\n        for c2 in range(3):\n            # Check if all prices can be paid with at most c1 ones and c2 twos\n            # and find minimum c3 needed\n            max_c3 = 0\n            feasible = True\n            for x in a:\n                # Find minimum c3 such that x can be paid with <=c1 ones, <=c2 twos, c3 threes\n                # x1 + 2*x2 + 3*x3 = x, x1<=c1, x2<=c2\n                min_c3 = float('inf')\n                for x1 in range(c1 + 1):\n                    for x2 in range(c2 + 1):\n                        rem = x - x1 - 2 * x2\n                        if rem >= 0 and rem % 3 == 0:\n                            min_c3 = min(min_c3, rem // 3)\n                if min_c3 == float('inf'):\n                    feasible = False\n                    break\n                max_c3 = max(max_c3, min_c3)\n            \n            if feasible:\n                best = min(best, c1 + c2 + max_c3)\n    \n    print(best)",
